							</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="circolo" class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
				<article class="glass-card hover-lift p-5">
					<span class="mb-2 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-800">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-4 w-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
							<rect x="4" y="6" width="16" height="12" rx="2" />
							<path d="M12 6v12M4 12h16" />
						</svg>
					</span>
					<h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Campi Padel</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">3 campi indoor di ultima generazione, disponibili tutto l'anno.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="glass-card hover-lift p-5">
					<span class="mb-2 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-800">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-4 w-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
							<path d="M7 16l4-4 3 3 4-4" />
							<circle cx="7" cy="16" r="1.5" />
							<circle cx="11" cy="12" r="1.5" />
							<circle cx="14" cy="15" r="1.5" />
							<circle cx="18" cy="11" r="1.5" />
						</svg>
					</span>
					<h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Lezioni</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Percorsi individuali e di gruppo per adulti e bambini, dal beginner all'agonista.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="glass-card hover-lift p-5">
					<span class="mb-2 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-800">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-4 w-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
							<path d="M4 8h16M4 12h16M4 16h10" />
							<circle cx="18" cy="16" r="2" />
						</svg>
					</span>
					<h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Tornei e Campionati</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Organizziamo eventi sociali e competizioni ufficiali durante tutto l'anno.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="glass-card hover-lift p-5">
					<span class="mb-2 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-800">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-4 w-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
							<circle cx="8" cy="10" r="2" />
							<circle cx="16" cy="10" r="2" />
							<path d="M4 18c.6-2.2 2.3-3.5 4-3.5S11.4 15.8 12 18M12 18c.6-2.2 2.3-3.5 4-3.5s3.4 1.3 4 3.5" />
						</svg>
					</span>
					<h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Community</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Un ambiente vivo dove trovare partner di gioco e nuove amicizie.</p>
				</article>
			</section>

			<section id="app" class="glass-card p-6 sm:p-8">
				<div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr] lg:items-center">
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-700">App dedicata</p>
						<h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Prenota i campi in autonomia dall'app</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-700 sm:text-base">
							Con l'app ufficiale puoi verificare disponibilita in tempo reale, prenotare i campi in pochi secondi e restare aggiornato su partite ed eventi del circolo.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-100 bg-white p-5">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Scarica l'app ufficiale Village Fregene Padel</p>
						<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Disponibile su App Store e Google Play.</p>
						<div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
							<a
								href="https://apps.apple.com/it/app/village-fregene-padel/id6740776472"
								target="_blank"
								rel="noopener noreferrer"
								aria-label="Scarica su App Store"
								class="inline-flex h-14 w-44 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md transition hover:opacity-90"
